Plot:

In a cyberpunk vision of the future, man has developed the technology to create replicants,
 human clones used to serve in the colonies outside Earth but with fixed lifespans. In Los
 Angeles, 2019, Deckard is a Blade Runner, a cop who specialises in terminating replicants.
 Originally in retirement, he is forced to re-enter the force when five replicants escape
 from an offworld colony to Earth.
